## DHCP Configuration and Network Automation

Configured a router as a DHCP server to dynamically assign IP addresses to multiple devices. 
Validated correct IP allocation, default gateway configuration, and DNS assignment.

### Key Skills:
- DHCP pool configuration
- Default gateway and DNS setup
- Troubleshooting IP assignment issues

### What I Learned:
This lab demonstrated how DHCP simplifies network management and how to diagnose issues when devices fail to receive IP addresses.
